title: S5 Ep13: Will Ukraine's economy survive the war?
itunes:title: Will Ukraine's economy survive the war?
description: Are the Ukrainian economy and financial system holding up to Russia's bombardment? Yevhenii Skok tells Tim Phillips whether emergency policies have been able to maintain liquidity and financial stability, how much damage has been done to Ukraine's productive capacity, and what a post-war financial rebuild would look like.
